1. In the "/etc/salt/master" add the following:

   extension_modules: /path/to/the/extension_pillar_modules

                                         ^
                                         |
2. Copy *.py from this directory here ---+


3. Then, in the "/etc/salt/master" add the following:

   ext_pillar:
     - suma_minion:
         prefix: server
         file_extension: sls
         overwrite: true
         environment: base
         pillar_roots:
           - /path/with/the/pillar/files
           - /another/path/with/the/pillar/files
